Class Title

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tectonica.jonix.onix2.Title
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OnixComposite, OnixComposite.OnixDataComposite<JonixTitle>, OnixComposite.OnixDataCompositeWithKey<JonixTitle,TitleTypes>, OnixTag, Serializable

    public class Title
extends Object
implements OnixComposite.OnixDataCompositeWithKey<JonixTitle,TitleTypes>, Serializable

    Title composite

    A repeatable group of data elements which together give the text of a title of a content item and specify its type, used here to give alternate forms of title for a content item. Please see Group PR.7 for details.

    Reference name<Title>
    Short tag<title>
